{"tid":2078931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偽造急救證並自稱牧師的姜嘉偉涉嫌恐嚇 香港教牧網絡亦發聲明澄清","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T14:22:49.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06ed09096fe738b50f9c787d6b423d1b1eda1c9e","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"今日上午，偽造急救證並自稱牧師的姜嘉偉pm本專頁，出言恐嚇。現將對話展示，大家可以判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmLZBs8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmLZBs8.jpg&h=16872230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我不是受害者。真正的受害者，是被他蒙在鼓裡的少年人。<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n補充資料<br />\nFA牧師姜嘉偉偽造急救證&mdash;&mdash;自按、自稱、自發的「三自牧師」<br />\n<a href=\"https://faith100.media/fakeung/66220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffaith100.media%2Ffakeung%2F66220&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=c42f53b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://faith100.media/fakeung/66220</a><br />\n<br />\n「耶教異聞錄357集，FA 牧師姜嘉偉身份之謎- 熱血時報網站連結 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/7/375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F7%2F375&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=219bb481\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/7/375</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020」（passionprime聽眾可收聽）<br />\n<br />\n和他對質的fb live<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dochanhk/videos/574315809941111/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdochanhk%2Fvideos%2F574315809941111%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=92945b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dochanhk/videos/574315809941111/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"9f445c95ea7e6b3da39fee1c32fcfa617eb29efa","tid":2078931,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"91403e704400bc899f591a8f063655841df5d4ed","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9i4NzZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9i4NzZ.png&h=d08060cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港教牧網絡 澄清聲明</strong><br />\n<br />\n從今天（2020年6月24日）網上一篇帖文*中有見姜嘉偉先生指「我今個星期五會見陳恩明同埋教牧聯網嘅人......」，本網絡特此澄清聲明：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港教牧網絡並沒有與姜嘉偉先生有任何見面約定，其言論與本網絡並無任何關係。我方亦對姜嘉偉先生的牧師身分、教導講論、神學背景存疑。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於原擬與他約見的陳恩明牧師亦因事未能成行。<br />\n<br />\n2020年6月24日<br />\n<br />\n*帖文連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/337355189653049/posts/2984004801654728/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F337355189653049%2Fposts%2F2984004801654728%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=f140b65f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/337355189653049/posts/2984004801654728/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b4c5533af60eb779e81a1c4ade4d98d004496298","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"香港教牧網絡Facebook澄清聲連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2323884767657341/posts/3144776002234876/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2323884767657341%2Fposts%2F3144776002234876%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=590df8ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2323884767657341/posts/3144776002234876/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7fb96cccf00b51484fe010f57ec7d6fe4a796772","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港教牧網絡Facebook澄清聲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明</span></strong>連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2323884767657341/posts/3144776002234876/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2323884767657341%2Fposts%2F3144776002234876%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=590df8ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2323884767657341/posts/3144776002234876/?d=n</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7cdb1a22b326ac746377ccaf083a668af765943b","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9729b6bf4910c0df9738eb182446d532cfa8705f","tid":2078931,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"點解耶撚一定係講弟兄姊妹﹐而唔係兄分姊妹?"},{"pid":"93b5cf510a70345ed483a646d8565200f32b4e35","tid":2078931,"uid":250550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"基督教參差不齊 <br />\n其實唔信好過信 <br />\n想博愛唔洗信教都可以做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357f4d28d680cbc4a1e2d655b1d111be275198ca","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9729b6bf4910c0df9738eb182446d532cfa8705f","tid":2078931,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"點解耶撚一定係講弟兄姊妹﹐而唔係兄分姊妹?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"翻譯問題，之後叫慣叫熟就冇改<br />\n<br />\n你用兄弟姊妹其實都ok"},{"pid":"674018151a939bd2b70737d3d61f6cd7854716f6","tid":2078931,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"357f4d28d680cbc4a1e2d655b1d111be275198ca","tid":2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9729b6bf4910c0df9738eb182446d532cfa8705f","tid":2078931,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"點解耶撚一定係講弟兄姊妹﹐而唔係兄分姊妹?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"翻譯問題，之後叫慣叫熟就冇改<br />\n<br />\n你用兄弟姊妹其實都ok"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:30:50.000Z","msg":