:2078931,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9729b6bf4910c0df9738eb182446d532cfa8705f","tid":2078931,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"點解耶撚一定係講弟兄姊妹﹐而唔係兄分姊妹?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"翻譯問題，之後叫慣叫熟就冇改<br />\n<br />\n你用兄弟姊妹其實都ok"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"邊度嘅翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港唔係一直叫開兄弟姊妹咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"你咁問成本聖經唔同版本嘅譯文都奇撚怪怪添<br />\n好多係一百幾十年前嘅翻譯，佢哋用下用下就照用到依家<br />\n<br />\n和合本Wiki：<br />\n語言 漢語（白話文）<br />\n新約出版時間 1906年<br />\n舊約出版時間 1918年<br />\n全書出版時間 1919年<br />\n譯者 狄考文（Calvin W. Mateer）、富善（Chauncey Goodrich）、鮑康寧（Frederick W. Baller）、文書田（George Owen）、鹿依士（Spencer Lewis）<br />\n<br />\n譯得好就奇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005846d90fc90d2f1be1db53decb78aa6d6346dc","tid":2078931,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A7%9C%E5%98%89%E5%81%89%E5%86%92%E7%A8%B1%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB-fa-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E7%A0%B4%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E8%AD%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A7%259C%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB-fa-%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%2589%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=22800d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25A7%259C%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB-fa-%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%2581%25BD